{"h8c793b1bg3761g4f15g91a2g004cc6148fdc": ["We wasted so much time fighting each other.", "96e41e71-9239-498b-9cb8-8b14fd48acd0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid2.html", "3257fa7a-0223-f276-4138-734e64e30f78"], "h9287d284g732fg4f2cga1b2gfe6d609a26ed": ["Silvanus taught us a lesson by letting an outsider save us.", "96e41e71-9239-498b-9cb8-8b14fd48acd0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid2.html", "90f3e921-877f-1412-bd1d-5a0331ac43d6"], "h7d560046g47d6g4419ga9d4g9bcc2ff70cfa": ["It'll take time to mend our grove. Thanks to you, we have it.", "96e41e71-9239-498b-9cb8-8b14fd48acd0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid2.html", "1d9a7821-21e7-07ae-d4bc-741924975d99"], "hd3206b2dg5711g45bdga33eg3ad61cb88525": ["Kagha lied to us. She <i>betrayed</i> us.", "96e41e71-9239-498b-9cb8-8b14fd48acd0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid2.html", "d360849e-8080-40d7-79cc-f6ff1e014fc5"], "h1963fc7bg670bg4593g9f5cg2398f3c2387c": ["She was a blight on the grove. You were right to put her down.", "96e41e71-9239-498b-9cb8-8b14fd48acd0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid2.html", "991fe31a-b10c-33c7-adf3-b0caf024591e"], "h25f3af68gbcc9g483cga9b8gf20e5dc62dc2": ["She didn't deserve your mercy.", "96e41e71-9239-498b-9cb8-8b14fd48acd0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid2.html", "913548c1-dc63-29c9-39a3-3c93f326549a"], "h41bc66d2g1f9ag4865gba5ag5f283522e048": ["Kagha fooled us. We're lucky you were here.", "96e41e71-9239-498b-9cb8-8b14fd48acd0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid2.html", "950691da-326b-cdae-f478-d1fadd27429e"], "h28935142g3463g4634g805bga0576fb144ba": ["<i>In umbram cretus, sanguine iuratus.</i>", "96e41e71-9239-498b-9cb8-8b14fd48acd0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid2.html", "e85a25f3-b159-dee4-b87a-4eabc4334b14"], "h9fc3c4ccgfac5g4ebbgb2bdg63a4fbd7090c": ["<i>Ab spiritu humoque, aculeus vitisque.</i>", "96e41e71-9239-498b-9cb8-8b14fd48acd0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid2.html", "90782d95-83c3-bcb9-614c-663931a54c40"], "h8cacef86g1ec7g44e2gad9dgf6f1860eee03": ["<i>Complexum tuum, ab terra ortum, ad nos defer.</i>", "96e41e71-9239-498b-9cb8-8b14fd48acd0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid2.html", "dfc58d42-502d-3f83-9484-40cee217395d"], "hc866ce95g40f4g438ega641g6e2cb3762bed": ["<i>Defende nos ab imminentibus aequilibrio tuo.</i>", "96e41e71-9239-498b-9cb8-8b14fd48acd0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid2.html", "16baf0fd-c9ff-8790-81a6-b0d087706158"], "hc8a72724ge578g4b90ga575gc68fddcfaa7a": ["<i>Hostes subeunt. Protege nos. Muni nos.</i>", "96e41e71-9239-498b-9cb8-8b14fd48acd0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid2.html", "839920ce-6cdf-d292-aabe-85358395e67b"], "ha9d94032gde7cg480egaf1bg9c6a4c5163dd": ["<i>Aggeniculamur in umbra tua, Pater Arborum.</i>", "96e41e71-9239-498b-9cb8-8b14fd48acd0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid2.html", "b087b4c3-4b29-2274-ddbf-aa52ce6b2278"]}